            "en-US": "* support for Thunderbird 78\n* fix display bug from version 0.1.3 (sorry for the inconvenience)\n* properly render markdown todo lists (- [ ], - [x]) with checkboxes\n\nIt might be necessary to restart thunderbird after updating the add-on due to a bug in previous versions.",
